游戏运送到该标题。 “预计三张大逃杀地图（包括第 04 季的新地图 Vondel）以及排名游戏、具有五个不同撤离区的 DMZ Beta、BlackCell 产品等都会有大量的游戏选择，”它写道。</p><p>不过，一些玩家并不满意，他们指出早期的大逃杀游戏（例如<em>《黑色行动 4》</em>中的<em>《Blackout》</em> ）仍然有运行的服务器，而最初的<em>《战区》</em>则没有。据<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://kotaku.com/call-of-duty-warzone-1-caldera-verdansk-shutdown-1850566598"><em>Kotaku 报道</em></a>，其他人对资源被分流到<em>《战区：移​​动》</em>感到不满，还有一些人指出他们将失去所有《战区》化妆品。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-original-call-of-duty-warzone-battle-royale-will-shut-down-in-september-125949437.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-original-call-of-duty-warzone-battle-royale-will-shut-down-in-september-125949437.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 2ebaf0c5-7cac-40d7-af68-6bd63bdde1d3</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jun 2023 12:59:49 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687525193</ingested><modified> 2023-06-23T12:59:56+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="493" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/5192cb50-11bd-11ee-bb7b-a6c79ae10aba" width="875"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="493" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023