 (ESA) 似乎对是否取消整个活动犹豫不决：“ESA 目前正在与 ESA 成员和其他利益相关者就 E3 2024（及以后）进行对话，”该组织告诉 Engadget。你仍然可以赶上<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/sgf-2023/">一切</a></ins>今年夏季游戏节上的非 E3，包括我们的第一印象<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sand-land-first-impressions-an-akira-toriyama-manga-brought-to-life-140023184.html"><em>沙地。</em></a></ins></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/e3-2024-and-2025-arent-canceled-yet-222141813.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-next-version-of-stable-diffusion-wont-produce-spaghetti-hands-171552952.html">下一版本的稳定扩散不会在 AI 图像中产生意大利面条手</a></h2><h3>有点刺耳。</h3><h3></h3><p>基于提示的 AI 图像生成器 Stable Diffusion 的下一版本将生成更加逼真的图像，并且更擅长使双手看起来不那么像恐怖表演。该公告出现在一篇后来被删除的博客文章中。 SDXL 0.9 是 Stable Diffusion XL 的后续版本，“与前身相比，图像和构图细节得到了大幅改进”，博客文章中写道。如果您有足够强大的计算机，SDXL 可以在您的 PC 上本地运行。它至少需要 16GB RAM 和具有 8GB VRAM 的 GeForce RTX 20（或更高版本）显卡。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-next-version-of-stable-diffusion-wont-produce-spaghetti-hands-171552952.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-plans-to-keep-making-smartphones-for-at-least-a-few-more-years-160051473.html">索尼计划至少在几年内继续生产智能手机</a></h2><h3>高通公司与索尼手机签订了一项多年期协议。</h3><figure> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-plans-to-keep-making-smartphones-for-at-least-a-few-more-years-160051473.html"><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/8aa7e490-11ac-11ee-acfe-f5f82a3d913e" style="height:482px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="2b750ea6-7f3c-342c-b6ac-144c9e66c64d"></a><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-plans-to-keep-making-smartphones-for-at-least-a-few-more-years-160051473.html">索尼</a></div></figure><p>你可能不会购买它们，但索尼将继续生产它们。索尼与高通达成了一项多年协议，将使用 Snapdragon 平台为其手机提供支持。这是现有协议的延伸。索尼上个月刚刚发布了其最新手机 Xperia 1 V。智能手机的目标受众再次是摄影师和视频博主。这些都是相对小众的用例，尽管索尼可以利用其相机技术来提供至少独特的东西。 Xperia 1 V 甚至可以用作兼容索尼 Alpha 相机的监视器。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-plans-to-keep-making-smartphones-for-at-least-a-few-more-years-160051473.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-zuckerberg-v-musk-the-cage-fight-111558709.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-zuckerberg-v-musk-the-cage-fight-111558709.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8d6e556e-6d6b-4c87-b728-76c63107ad8e</guid><dc:creator>马特·史密斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jun 2023 11:15:58 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687514538</ingested><modified> 2023-06-23T10:02:28+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="708" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/bd06cf90-10d6-11ee-bff9-ea29d1c00152" width="1066"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="708" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/bd06cf90-10d6-11ee-bff9-ea29d1c00152" width="1066"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Mark Zuckerberg]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Two people in a fight, one has the other in a headlock. There's an audience behind them.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Mark Zuckerberg]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ford secures $9.2 billion loan from US Department of Energy to build EV battery factories]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>美国政府重申其将电动汽车生产转移到本土而不是依赖外国实体的承诺。 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-ford-ev-battery-plant-funding-biden-green-technology/?sref=10lNAhZ9"><em>据彭博社</em>报道，</a>美国能源部贷款计划办公室 (LPO) 宣布向福特和韩国电池生产商 SK On 旗下的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.energy.gov/lpo/articles/lpo-announces-conditional-commitment-loan-blueoval-sk-further-expand-us-ev-battery">BlueOval SK (BOSK) 提供 92 亿美元有条件贷款</a>，用于建设三座电池制造厂。</p><p>这笔贷款是 LPO 迄今为止发放的最大一笔贷款，几乎是去年<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-energy-department-loan-ev-battery-manufacturing-190736000.html">为通用汽车和 LG 合资企业 Ultium Cell 提供的 25 亿美元贷款</a>的四倍。贷款规模的部分原因是去年《通货膨胀削减法案》的通过，该法案导致 LPO 的贷款预算增加至 4000 亿美元。就背景而言，在过去 14 年中，LPO 分散了约 330 亿美元。要实现拜登-哈里斯政府到 2030 年电动汽车占美国汽车销量一半的目标，额外的资本肯定是必要的。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>肯塔基州将有两家工厂，田纳西州将有一家，这三家工厂都为福特和林肯即将推出的电动汽车生产电池。该汽车制造商今年早些时候还宣布了<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ford-reportedly-plans-to-build-a-35-billion-ev-battery-plant-in-michigan-213730306.html">在密歇根州建设磷酸铁锂电池工厂</a>的计划。福特的目标是到 2026 年推出 200 万辆电动汽车，其中全电动 Explorer、野马 Mach-E 和 E-Transit 已经上市，林肯的电动汽车系列也正在开发中，福特的产量也在增加。相比之下，福特在 2022 年生产了约 132,000 辆电动汽车。福特最近还确保其电动汽车驾驶员<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ford-ev-drivers-will-get-access-to-12000-north-american-tesla-superchargers-next-spring-221752191.html">能够使用北美各地的 12,000 个特斯拉充电站</a>。</p><p> LPO 强调，这笔贷款还将为该地区带来就业机会，一旦工厂开始运营，将创造 5,000 个建筑工作岗位和另外 7,500 个运营工作岗位。这项投资还符合<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/epa-environmental-justice-civil-rights-office-082419537.html">拜登总统的 Justice40 倡议</a>，即 40% 的特定联邦投资（包括 LPO 贷款）流向弱势社区。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/ford-secures-92-billion-loan-from-us-department-of-energy-to-build-ev-battery-factories-102520341.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/ford-secures-92-billion-loan-from-us-department-of-energy-to-build-ev-battery-factories-102520341.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ff20f928-e16b-4040-90b0-84aa9ddf10f0</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jun 2023 10:25:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687515004</ingested><modified> 2023-06-23T10:10:08+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Loans]]></category><category><![CDATA[Finance]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="2347" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/615024c0-72c8-11eb-b7ff-b7c42a7481b8" width="4032"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2347" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/615024c0-72c8-11eb-b7ff-b7c42a7481b8" width="4032"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Andrew Tarantola / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Ford Mach-E EV in white parked in a lot by a park.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Ford Mach-E]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss